00:30:52,141 --> 00:30:54,269
Isn't that fine then?

269
00:30:54,811 --> 00:30:57,897
What is the conclusion you came up with?

270
00:30:57,981 --> 00:30:59,482
but…

271
00:31:01,067 --> 00:31:04,821
you will definitely regret it

272
00:31:08,449 --> 00:31:12,203
I can say that because I have never struggled with money.

273
00:31:14,789 --> 00:31:19,711
Once you get it, you'll be obsessed with it.

274
00:31:29,304 --> 00:31:30,888
do your best

275
00:31:35,977 --> 00:31:37,061
Excuse me

276
00:32:08,301 --> 00:32:09,802
knock)

277
00:32:10,887 --> 00:32:12,180
Yes

278
00:32:16,601 --> 00:32:17,977
yes

279
00:32:25,276 --> 00:32:28,780
(Fuyu) I think this is my duty.

280
00:32:30,531 --> 00:32:33,534
I'm well aware that it's brazen, but...

281
00:32:36,037 --> 00:32:38,456
I will give it to you

282
00:33:08,695 --> 00:33:10,071
(Seiichiro) “Yukiya”

283
00:33:11,364 --> 00:33:15,743
“There’s one thing I couldn’t tell you the other day.”

284
00:33:20,581 --> 00:33:23,251
“You might say it’s too late, but⸺”

285
00:33:25,878 --> 00:33:30,967
“You told me so harshly that I became afraid to talk.”

286
00:33:34,095 --> 00:33:35,555
“Sorry”

287
00:33:39,225 --> 00:33:40,518
“When I see you again⸺”

288
00:33:40,601 --> 00:33:42,603
“I might not be able to say it⸺”

289
00:33:43,229 --> 00:33:45,523
“I decided to tell you by letter.”

290
00:33:47,692 --> 00:33:48,943
“That day⸺”

291
00:33:50,069 --> 00:33:51,154
“The day of the fire”

292
00:33:51,237 --> 00:33:53,406
- (Male) Don't go, no... - (Yukiya as a child) Mother!

293
00:33:53,489 --> 00:33:54,365
Mother!

294
00:34:21,142 --> 00:34:23,269
-(Saori) Dinner is ready! -(Boy) Lunch!

295
00:34:23,352 --> 00:34:26,230
-(Boy) Huh? -(Saori) Look!

296
00:34:26,314 --> 00:34:27,482
(Yukiya) It’s me⸺

297
00:34:27,565 --> 00:34:30,443
When I grow up, I'll be like my mother

298
00:34:31,778 --> 00:34:33,029
(Saori) Huh...

299
00:34:37,116 --> 00:34:39,160
(Seiichiro) “To someone who shouldn’t be seen⸺”

300
00:34:40,036 --> 00:34:42,789
“Saori and I were seen.”

301
00:34:56,010 --> 00:35:01,015
“There was a look of disappointment and disappointment on my son’s face.”

302
00:35:01,849 --> 00:35:05,561
“I could see it clearly.”

303
00:35:05,645 --> 00:35:07,021
- (Saori) Follow me- (Seiichiro) But...

304
00:35:07,105 --> 00:35:09,065
(Saori) Please, please go home already.

305
00:35:09,565 --> 00:35:10,399
Please

306
00:35:11,275 --> 00:35:16,280
(Seiichiro) “That day I broke my son.”

307
00:35:21,035 --> 00:35:23,788
“It’s not atonement, but…”

308
00:35:40,847 --> 00:35:44,058
“What I could have done at that time⸺”

309
00:35:45,434 --> 00:35:47,436
“Protecting Masayuki”

310
00:35:48,062 --> 00:35:50,857
“All I wanted to do was protect the Ise family.”

311
00:36:05,830 --> 00:36:07,331
My mother is⸺

312
00:36:10,751 --> 00:36:12,753
It wasn't suicide

313
00:36:17,675 --> 00:36:19,302
My brother...

314
00:36:22,221 --> 00:36:23,806
My brother...

315
00:36:26,184 --> 00:36:28,394
(Seiichiro) “I won’t ask you to forgive me.”

316
00:36:28,477 --> 00:36:30,605
“I don’t even ask you to understand.”

317
00:36:31,522 --> 00:36:33,482
“I just⸺”

318
00:36:34,984 --> 00:36:37,403
“I just wanted to protect it.”

319
00:36:38,863 --> 00:36:41,407
“It’s all my fault.”

320
00:36:42,116 --> 00:36:46,829
“I am fully responsible for Masayuki’s sins.”

321
00:36:47,747 --> 00:36:48,748
‪♪～

322
00:36:48,831 --> 00:36:53,044
“I don’t care if you hate me as much as you want.”

323
00:36:54,670 --> 00:36:57,673
Wow!

324
00:37:22,990 --> 00:37:26,202
(screams)

325
00:37:43,970 --> 00:37:47,306
(Yukiya) He killed my mother and stole my wife.

326
00:37:47,390 --> 00:37:48,391
‪～♪

327
00:37:48,474 --> 00:37:52,812
The man who took everything from my life

328
00:37:53,688 --> 00:37:54,730
(stinging sound)

329
00:37:58,567 --> 00:37:59,860
Fuu…

330
00:37:59,944 --> 00:38:02,154
I don't care what happens now

331
00:38:03,030 --> 00:38:05,533
Destroy Masayuki Ise

332
00:38:06,534 --> 00:38:10,413
I won't forgive you

333
00:38:13,332 --> 00:38:16,002
(Yukiya) Why did you light the fire? Why did you kill me?

334
00:38:16,085 --> 00:38:17,503
(Masayuki) It doesn't matter to me!

335
00:38:17,586 --> 00:38:20,006
(Erika) If this goes out into the world, it will be the end of the Ise family.

336
00:38:20,089 --> 00:38:20,965
laughter)

337
00:38:21,048 --> 00:38:23,634
I didn't think it could be used this much

338
00:38:23,718 --> 00:38:25,094
Thank you so far

339
00:38:25,177 --> 00:38:27,805
 (Yukiya) Welcome to the real hell
